summary: This file was made for users, who have trouble building/seeing Windstad Manor, while using awesome Real Wildlife mod.
descriptionHtml: Using TESVEdit I've overwritten 3 Real wildlife records, that conflicted with Hearthifres plugin and prevented Windstad Manor from being seen and/or built by the player. I don't see any bugs with this patch, but playtesting is welcome.
author: badger45
